link_desc:
This is a modified version of the template found https://www.zabbix.com/forum/showthread.php?t=8074

Linked to SNMP Generic, SNMP Interfaces and ICMP Ping to expand the useful data.

Graph added for supply levels.

Trigger for supply levels modified to include "Information" severity level.

Triggers modified for supply value being 0 ~ 100.

Tested on HP m277dw

Version uploaded for 4.x. Removed ICMP Ping link. Updated the name.
